Console.WriteLine(serialized)
// {"Person":{"HasValue":true,"Value":{"FirstName":null,"Age":null,"Birthday":null}}} (Actual)
// {"Person":{"FirstName":null,"Age":null,"Birthday":null}} (Expected)
```

Deserialization (Debug)
```C#
